pg-dbms-lock (2.0-1PIGSTY) unstable; urgency=medium

  * Initial package for pg_dbms_lock 2.0.
  * Build version-specific packages for PostgreSQL 14 through 18.
  * Adapt named lock allocation to pg_background 2.x and declare the database
    extension prerequisite.
  * Stabilize the asynchronous upstream multi-session test.
  * Verify source integrity and prevent stale build artifacts.
  * Install the upstream changelog through dh_installchangelogs.

